quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Say: “O unbelievers!”",footnotes:182871:1
  109,2,"I do not worship those that you worship",footnotes:182872:1
  109,3,"neither do you worship Him Whom I worship;",footnotes:182873:1
  109,4,"nor will I worship those whom you have worshipped;"
  109,5,"nor are you going to worship Him Whom I worship.",footnotes:182874:1
  109,6,"To you is your religion, and to me, my religion.",footnotes:182875:1
